               <rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_1666"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__peter_waicz_QGW_II_I_1666">Peter der Waicz, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">purger</roleName> ze
                  Wienn</rs></rs>, <triggerstring n="disp">verkauft</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="disp">mit Handen</triggerstring> des <rs type="person" ref="#pe__rudolf_angerfelder_QGW_II_I_1335"><roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">Bürgermeisters</roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Rudolfs des Angerfelder</rs> und <rs type="org" ref="#org__wien">des rats gemain der stat ze Wienn</rs></rs> ein
                  Haus, <rs type="event" ref="NULL">das er <rs type="person" ref="#pe__jakob_wachsgiesser_QGW_II_I_1403">Jacoben, dem <roleName type="prof">wachsgiesser</roleName></rs>, vor offem gericht in der
